OL,7,FLewis Hamilton has been disqualified
OL,8,Ffrom sixth place in the Chinese Grand
OL,9,FPrix after his Ferrari was adjudged to
OL,10,Fhave broken the rules.
OL,12,FHamilton, who had scored eight points,
OL,13,Fwas summoned to see the stewards in
OL,14,FShanghai after the rearmost skid on
OL,15,Fhis Ferrari came in between 8.5 and
OL,16,F8.6 millimetres, which is less than
OL,17,Fthe 9mm minimum thickness required.
