OL,3,CLewis Hamilton and Charles Leclerc
OL,4,Cdisqualified in nightmare race for
OL,5,CFerrari
OL,7,FThree hours after the race Hamilton
OL,8,Fwas thrown out of the result, with
OL,9,FFerrari team-mate Charles Leclerc also
OL,10,Fdisqualified from fifth place after
OL,11,Fhis car was underweight.
OL,13,FAlpine's Pierre Gasly has also been
OL,14,Fexpelled for the same breach.
OL,16,FThe stewards said in a statement: "The
OL,17,Fplank assembly of Car 44 (Hamilton)
OL,18,Fwas measured and found to be 8.6mm
OL,19,F(LHS), 8.6mm (car centerline) and
OL,20,F8.5mm (RHS).
