OL,3,CLewis Hamilton and Charles Leclerc
OL,4,Cdisqualified in nightmare race for
OL,5,CFerrari
OL,7,F"This is below the minimum thickness
OL,8,Fof 9mm specified under Article 3.5.9
OL,9,Fof the Technical Regulations."
OL,11,FDuring the hearing the team
OL,12,Frepresentative confirmed that the
OL,13,Fmeasurement is correct and that all
OL,14,Frequired procedures were performed
OL,15,Fcorrectly.
OL,17,FThe team also acknowledged that there
OL,18,Fwere no mitigating circumstances and
OL,19,Fthat it was a genuine error by the
OL,20,Fteam.
