OL,3,CLewis Hamilton and Charles Leclerc
OL,4,Cdisqualified in nightmare race for
OL,5,CFerrari
OL,7,F"The stewards determine that Article
OL,8,F3.5.9 of the FIA Formula 1 Technical
OL,9,FRegulations has been breached and
OL,10,Ftherefore the standard penalty of a
OL,11,Fdisqualification needs to be applied
OL,12,Ffor such an infringement."
OL,14,FOscar Piastri went on to win the
OL,15,FChinese Grand Prix, with Lando Norris
OL,16,Ffollowing his team-mate home as
OL,17,FMcLaren underlined their impressive
OL,18,Fspeed by executing a one-two finish.
